text: Vital Heynen (born 12 June 1969) is a former Belgian volleyball player and head coach of German club VfB Friedrichshafen and Poland men's national volleyball team. Since 2024, he serves as head coach for the China national team.https://sporza.be/nl/2024/04/24/vital-heynen-kiest-voor-oosters-avontuur- belgisch-volleybalbrein-gaat-aan-de-slag-als-bondscoach-van- china~1713973527134/ ==References == Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian volleyball players Category:Volleyball coaches Category:People from Limburg (Belgium)
